data.description: This BRICK, private END UNIT townhome is perfect. Be very proud to come home to the spacious feeling open floor plan with new stylish laminate flooring, neutral paint throughout, and a gas Fireplace. Even has something the rest of them don't; a BONUS ROOM for an office or exercise. The yard is just the right size to enjoy and it's FENCED. Evenings on the patio grilling out with friends will create sweet moments. All that's missing is you!
